'''Kalyani Varadarajan''' (October 1926 – October 2003), commonly known as Kalyani, is one of [[Carnatic music]]'s famous twentieth-century composers. She has created carnatic compositions in all 72 [[melakarta]] [[raga]]s, besides scores of [[janya]] ragas. [[File:Kalyani Varadarajan.jpg|alt=Kalyani Varadarajan|thumb|Kalyani Varadarajan playing veena some time during the 1950s]]
==Early life==
